name: Windows 10 Configurer
body:
Windows 10 Configurer is a free program that allows you to quickly remove Windows 10 default apps and install the legacy Windows Photo Viewer.

## Downloads

[Latest Version](https://github.com/WilliamVenner/win10configurer/releases/download/1/win10configurer.zip)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
